profile:
The way your property looks on the outside is important, and at BDR Property Maintenance, we understand this. And we also understand that you don’t have the time or the energy to spend making sure your residential or commercial property looks pristine throughout the year. This is why we are proud to offer landscaping and yard maintenance services in the Simcoe County, Ontario area that are complemented by competitive rates and customized contracts.With our landscaping services, we’ll keep your commercial or residential property in top shape all year round.

***

When we say we can maintain your property throughout the year, we really mean it! Whether you need us to take over your property maintenance tasks in the fall, spring, summer, or winter, we can do it. We also offer annual, seasonal, monthly, and one-time contracts. We’d be more than happy to give you a free estimate, as well, so you can get a better feel for what we can do for you.

***

We provide annual, seasonal, and monthly residential and commercial landscaping services in Simcoe County, ON. We are a family owned and operated business. We take pride in our work! We are committed to quality, and we stand behind everything we do! When you leave your property maintenance needs up to us, we won’t leave things half done. Rather, we’ll go above and beyond to make sure you are completely satisfied with how your yard and landscaping look.
